dct_title_s: Ordnance Survey of England and Wales: popular edition one-inch map. Llandudno & Denbigh. Sheet 42
dct_description_sm: Revision 1918-19. Alternate panel title: Ordnance Survey contoured road map of Llandudno & Denbigh. Sheet 42. Relief shown by 50 feet contour intervals and spot elevation. Surveyed in 1870-88.
